<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Customer Form</title>
    <style>
        body, table, td, a {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
            line-height: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 580px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .buttonform {
            background-color: #5bc928;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: gray;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table class="container" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="background-color: rgb(66, 66, 66); ">
                            <img src="cid:image1" alt="MailAmericas header" style="width: 100%; display: block;">
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 20px;">
                            <h2 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Hello, {{nickname or name}}!</h2>
                            <p>{{name}}, you have been registered to our portal so you can track and create your
                                invoices.</p>
                            <p>To get started, simply click on the link below:</p>
                            <a class="buttonform" style="color: white;text-decoration: none;" href="#LINK_FORM#">Go to portal</a>
                            <p>Your login details:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    Username: {{nickname or email}}
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Password:  {{initial_password}}
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance with using the portal, please feel free to reach
                                out to us at <a href="mailto:providersportal@mailamericas.com">providersportal@mailamericas.com</a></p>
                            <p>Best regards,</p>
                            <p>The MailAmericas Team</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="background-color: rgb(66, 66, 66);">
                            <img src="cid:image2" alt="MailAmericas footer" style="width: 100%; display: block;">
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="footer">
                            MailAmericas | Guemes 676 | Vicente LÃ³pez | 1638
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>